---
title: "US25 — Join challenges + earn rewards"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ChallengeDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>JoinChallenge
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SocialGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: tap JOIN CHALLENGE
  B->>C: join(challengeId)
  C->>G: insert challenge_participants
  alt joined
    G-->>C: ok
    C-->>B: participating
    B-->>A: progress tracked - XP on completion
  else deadline passed
    G-->>C: rejected
    B-->>A: "Challenge has ended"
  end
  note over C,G: rewards = XP / levels<br/>(replaces badges - schema v2)
